In the INTEREST OF K.P. and A.B., Minor Children, J.P., Father of K.P., Appellant, B.B., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1872 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother and father appeal the termination of their parental rights in their children. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
